# 🔒 Encrypted Notes & Diary with AI ✨  
A secure, AI-powered diary that encrypts notes and provides **Summarization, Sentiment Analysis, and Keyword Extraction** features.

## 🚀 Features
- 🛡 **AES Encryption**: Ensures all notes are securely stored.
- 📝 **Summarization**: Generates short summaries of long diary entries.
- 😊 **Sentiment Analysis**: Detects emotions in notes.
- 🔍 **Keyword Extraction**: Highlights important topics automatically.
- 🎨 **Modern UI**: A sleek and user-friendly interface built with **PyQt**.

