🛠 Requirements (Dependencies)
PyQt6==6.6.1
textblob==0.18.0
nltk==3.8.1
pycryptodome==3.20.0
🤖 AI Features
Summarization: Uses nltk to generate short summaries.

Sentiment Analysis: Detects emotions in diary entries.

Keyword Extraction: Uses spaCy to highlight important topics.

🎯 How to Use
1️⃣ Open the app and log in securely.
2️⃣ Write a note and click "Encrypt & Save".
3️⃣ Use AI features: Click "Summarize", "Analyze Sentiment", or "Extract Keywords".
4️⃣ Retrieve & Decrypt Notes anytime securely.

📌 Future Enhancements
🌐 Cloud backup for encrypted notes.

